title: Am I the only person not able to do the "The Teemoing" flash game?

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body: Not sure if i am just an idiot or my flash game is bugged. I click the button and it doesnt go up. Thought? Opinions? Thanks!

replies.body: As a rule of thumb, if you ever think you might be the only person chances are you're not! :P  It looks like something is blocking the site from interacting, which could be happening for a few reasons like extension or caching problems.  As a first step, I recommend [clearing your cache.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies)  You can also try playing this in Incognito or another browser entirely to make sure it can load properly.  Hopefully, that fixes things up so you can summon the little mischief!
